Package org.eolang.jeo.representation.bytecode

Class BytecodeLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eolang.jeo.representation.bytecode.BytecodeLine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BytecodeEntry
    public final class BytecodeLine
extends Object
implements BytecodeEntry
    Bytecode line. This class represents the reference to a source line from a bytecode instruction. Since the purpose of this class is rather informative, we just ignore it.
    Since:
    0.6
